data.description: Spacious 4 BR, 5 Bth, 1-1/2 story loaded with updates from Kitchen to Baths, Granite countertops, tiled backsplash, vessel sinks, laminate floors, Oak stairs, and more. New exterior and interior stonework, maintenance free vinyl siding, and modern double pane replacement windows throughout. One master BR on the main floor and a second one upstairs. More finished space in the full Basement. Enjoy the beautifully landscaped yard and feel of privacy on partially covered expansive deck nearly year round.
